  "text": "Our quantization is applied during fine-tuning after training a full-precision network. As the baseline, we adopt the fine-tuning procedure in [CITATION_1] , where we perform incremental/progressive quantization. In contrast to [CITATION_2] , we first quantize activations and then weights in an incremental quantization. In addition, for each precision configuration, we perform teacher-student training to improve the quantized network [CITATION_3] .",
